com.vmware.nsx.node.services

Class ServicesFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vmware.nsx.node.services.ServicesFactory

  • public class ServicesFactory
extends Object
    ServicesFactory is responsible for creating instances of services contained inside the com.vmware.nsx.node.services package and also has the subpackages reference to access respective subpackage services.
